{"type": "article", "id": 28993, "title": "树杈衣架", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-01T06:49:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 64, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703125343uYCL1hH2skNEMSlW.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>来自瑞士的 <a href=\"http://www.klybeck.net/\">Klybeck</a> 是一家成立于 2013 年的家具设计公司，Ivy 是旗下的一款衣架，每组包含三种不同的形状，通过金属底座和螺丝固定后可以用来悬挂衣物或者雨伞。当几组衣架错落地布置在墙上时，会带给人一种仿佛置身于大自然中的错觉。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703125341CpwnVBflAgDP5324.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703125342jriSa2XGo698wJtB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59861111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070312534267wJRIAd9p1o4NMT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703125343Gsdv6bD1O5ryUhT9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74861111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}